{
  "stem": "747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she felt full with hatred and misery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my-- one of my friends find out that she's working there, went to her, and said, listen, if we leave our friend here, she will never make it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can you do something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, what's her name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after got my name, she went and she was cleaning there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the Nazis weren't around, she just pulled out my file from one batch, and pulled out someone else's, and put mine back to the one who went in the transport.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she send a message to me that I should be out with the group at 6:00 in the morning, before they are starting to send the transport away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a good pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I give it to her, and gave me a wooden clog instead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took my-- I had a good sweater, and my friends, also, whatever they had, give it to her because we-- that was we could pay her kindness.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I will stay here, out in the morning, and the whole night I didn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they finally called my name, I was so relieved that now, maybe, I have a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just I know she was from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know names, which was just faces, you know, just friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they took us on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We traveled the whole day, and full-- and then at nighttime, we arrived to a station, and it was about--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were under observation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there was something that I remember very clearly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before we--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
